          <p class='first-para'>
            You want to group Amendment No. 103A with which amendment?
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0660P0-03311'>
        <a name='S5LV0660P0_20040429_GCR_43'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-merlin-hay' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0660P0_20040429_GCR_43' title='Link to this speech by Mr Merlin Hay' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
