            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_129gc' title='Col. 129GC &mdash; HL Deb 29 April 2004 vol 660 c129GC' name='column_129gc' href='#column_129gc' rel='bookmark'>129GC</a>
            they will be used. That is another matter under discussion by the group that is considering the regulations and the best way in which to proceed.
          </p>
